oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Postpartum use of Lutalyse*/Dinolytic* Sterile Solution in Problem Cows
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Luchsinger, J. H.
Boucher, J. F.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: reproductive performance
problem cows
postpartum
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: To evaluate the effect of Lutalyse/Dinolytic on future reproductive performance when administered to problem cows postpartum either once on days 21-28, or twice on days 21-28 and again 14 days later, when compared to non-treated control cows.
